{
  "stem": "24171.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I was kind of nibbling on that cabbage, and I got an upset stomach.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I got sick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So but I went to work the next day and the next day, and then I was complaining for the [GERMAN] that somehow I don't feel good, if it's possible, I should stay, because I was not allowed to stay in the-- in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Just those stayed there which came from that [GERMAN], it called, from the hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they stayed a few days till they were assigned somewhere else to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then-- so she said, if you want to go to [GERMAN], I'll give you a slip, and there and there it is, and I have it there on that piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I went there, and we were kind of so established in the camp, so we were not be afraid that we were going to be, like, separated, because we could see each other.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I went there, and they-- every afternoon, after they came home from work, they came there by the fence.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was laying by the window because I was asking, could I have my sisters.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I always said that they are my sisters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I never said that they are, you know, nieces or things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Just we are sisters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I had a window there that-- to lay there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I got white bread, that was the diet, and some kind of white-- like navy beans, something like that for the food, not more-- more than the outside, but kind of better a little bit.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember if I got some aspirin or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember what they did.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
